comments: Harrell (LAC) briefly grasps Adams' (OKC) arm during the rebound but the contact does not affect his ability to go for the ball.
Ferguson (OKC) places a hand/arm to the front of Williams (LAC) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Grant (OKC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Beverley (LAC) and absorbs the contact.
After Beverley (LAC) disengages from the pick he wraps Grant (OKC) around the waist as he moves towards the basket.
LLS shows Westbrook (OKC) extends his leg as part of a natural shooting motion on the jump shot attempt and Gallinari (LAC) legally contests the shot without making contact.
Adams (OKC) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Schroder (OKC) makes marginal contact with Gallinari (LAC) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
[Observable in enhanced video] Gallinari (LAC) slides his pivot foot.
Schroder (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position on Gallinari (LAC) during the drive.
Beverley (LAC) briefly places an arm around Grant (OKC) following the pick but he immediately disengages.
LLB and LAR show that Gallinari (LAC) establishes himself in a legal guarding position in Westbrook's (OKC) path and Westbrook drives through and dislodges him.
Gallinari (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Schroder (OKC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LLS shows Williams (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position on Schroder (OKC) and he cleanly steals the ball.
Schroder (OKC) commits a take foul on Williams (LAC).
Adams (OKC) makes incidental contact with Harrell (LAC) on the rebound.
LLS shows Beverley (LAC) grabs and pulls Ferguson's (OKC) jersey shorts during the upward shooting motion of his jump shot attempt.
Nader (OKC) briefly places an arm around the back of Shamet (LAC) but he removes it and the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Grant (OKC) makes clean contact with the ball while defending Gallinari (LAC).
Schroder (OKC) commits a take foul on Gallinari (LAC).
Adams (OKC) commits a take foul on Gallinari (LAC).
